Package: vastRapp
Title: VAST Interactive Builder
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luebber", "Finn", email = "f.luebber2@uni-luebeck.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0893-2120"))
    )
Description: An interactive Shiny application for building, comparing, and
    translating Visual Argument Structure Tool (VAST) models. Provides a
    visual interface for constructing VAST diagrams, AI-assisted translation
    between narrative theory text and formal VAST representations, and
    theory rigor assessment. Part of the VAST ecosystem alongside 'vastR'
    (core model construction and rendering) and 'vastRai' (AI bridge layer).
